================================================================================
  SHA-3 HARDWARE ACCELERATOR  --  OPTION A (MEMORY-MAPPED) INTEGRATION
  Detailed README
================================================================================

  Integrating an iterative SHA3-256 core into a 32-bit, 5-stage RISC-V
  pipeline using memory-mapped I/O. The CPU drives the accelerator with
  ordinary lw / sw instructions -- the same instructions it uses for RAM.

  Verified in simulation (Icarus Verilog): both the wrapper unit test and the
  full pipeline-driven program produce the correct SHA3-256("abc") digest.

  Target digest:
    SHA3-256("abc") =
    3a985da74fe225b2045c172d6bd390bd855f086e3e9d525b46bfe24511431532


